<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 18:08:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 128 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-128/0000018d-9943-d92c-a9ed-fbfbeb7b0000</link><description>据报道，埃及警告哈马斯，在以色列国防军拉法之前，它有两周时间与以色列达成停火协议，但埃及还威胁称，如果以色列向以色列发动地面进攻，将暂停与以色列的和平条约。 哈马斯高级官员：对拉法的任何袭击都将结束人质谈判释放协议 ■ 巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯飞往卡塔尔，与总理阿勒萨尼讨论战后加沙的前景 ■ 战争结束 128 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 17:47:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-128/0000018d-9943-d92c-a9ed-fbfbeb7b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属向国际刑事法院提出针对哈马斯领导人的索赔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-lodge-claim-against-hamas-leaders-to-intl-criminal-court/0000018d-98de-dc01-a9cf-9affceb50000</link><description>已获释的人质以及仍被关押在加沙的人质亲属将飞往海牙，在国际刑事法院提供此案证词，该法院部分寻求对哈马斯领导人发出逮捕令</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 17:15:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-lodge-claim-against-hamas-leaders-to-intl-criminal-court/0000018d-98de-dc01-a9cf-9affceb50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列定居者建立西岸前哨基地；其他人在另一起事件中袭击巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-erect-west-bank-outpost-others-attack-palestinians-in-separate-incident/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfb721d0000</link><description>以色列国防消息人士怀疑政府是否会撤离建在国家控制土地上的前哨基地 ■ 大约 15 名以色列人袭击了西岸北部的巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 16:25:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settlers-erect-west-bank-outpost-others-attack-palestinians-in-separate-incident/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfb721d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长：政府有关国内问题的决定非法通过，必须重新考虑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-govt-decisions-on-domestic-issues-were-illegally-passed-must-be-reconsidered/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfbdcf70000</link><description>几项政府私营部门决议的通过没有适当的专业和法律基础，甚至存在法律障碍。代表总检察长发出的一封信命令政府在额外审议中重新考虑这些问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 16:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-govt-decisions-on-domestic-issues-were-illegally-passed-must-be-reconsidered/0000018d-9893-d92c-a9ed-fbfbdcf70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列指控哈马斯关系后，约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人担心近东救济工程处关闭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/cutting-off-aid-will-hurt-many-people-west-bank-palestinians-fear-unrwa-closure/0000018d-98af-db74-a1ef-dbef17660000</link><description>该联合国机构为约旦河西岸约 87 万巴勒斯坦人提供服务，运营着 96 所学校和 43 个初级医疗机构。巴勒斯坦人担心如果该机构的资金不恢复将会发生什么</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 15:50:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/cutting-off-aid-will-hurt-many-people-west-bank-palestinians-fear-unrwa-closure/0000018d-98af-db74-a1ef-dbef17660000</guid></item><item><title>庆祝哈马斯，针对犹太人：在埃尔多安的土耳其，加沙战争营造了一种危险的气氛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/celebrating-hamas-targeting-jews-in-turkey-the-gaza-war-is-triggering-a-dangerous-mood/0000018d-985e-db74-a1ef-db5e069c0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日大屠杀以来，土耳其发生了一系列反以色列抗议和事件，这些抗议和事件有时不符合逻辑，但显然是受到总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 信息的启发</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 15:49:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/celebrating-hamas-targeting-jews-in-turkey-the-gaza-war-is-triggering-a-dangerous-mood/0000018d-985e-db74-a1ef-db5e069c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的经济表现相当不错。那么，是什么在吞噬穆迪呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-economy-is-doing-pretty-well-so-whats-eating-moodys/0000018d-9897-dc01-a9cf-9aff5f0a0000</link><description>穆迪下调以色列信用评级的原因只有一件事：不确定性——而且不仅仅是加沙战争的不确定性。政府的反应不是倾听，而是愤怒和空洞的保证</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 14:44:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-economy-is-doing-pretty-well-so-whats-eating-moodys/0000018d-9897-dc01-a9cf-9aff5f0a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府将在超级碗期间投放广告呼吁释放人质父亲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-to-run-ads-calling-for-release-of-hostage-fathers-in-u-s-during-super-bowl/0000018d-984e-db74-a1ef-db4e865d0000</link><description>这些广告包括电视、广播和广告牌广告，总理办公室称这些广告的观看次数已达 1000 万次，将在全国观看超级碗比赛时在美国媒体上播放</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 14:22:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-to-run-ads-calling-for-release-of-hostage-fathers-in-u-s-during-super-bowl/0000018d-984e-db74-a1ef-db4e865d0000</guid></item><item><title>官员称，如果以色列推进拉法，埃及威胁将暂停重要和平条约</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/egypt-threatens-to-suspend-key-peace-treaty-if-israel-pushes-into-rafah-officials-say/0000018d-97e0-d443-a19f-fff1e5c50000</link><description>埃及官员担心，以色列对拉法的军事进攻（据称这是击败哈马斯所必需的）将给埃及带来灾难性的人道主义局势和可能的难民危机</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 11:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/egypt-threatens-to-suspend-key-peace-treaty-if-israel-pushes-into-rafah-officials-say/0000018d-97e0-d443-a19f-fff1e5c50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列借战争掩护，计划在东耶路撒冷建立犹太人新社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/under-the-cover-of-war-israel-is-moving-to-build-a-new-jewish-neighborhood-in-east-jlem/0000018d-9786-d9cc-a5cd-f7be43b10000</link><description>Nofei Rachel 是计划在东耶路撒冷为犹太人增加 3,000 个新住宅单元的四个街区之一。近年来，司法部已成为推进这些犹太社区建设计划的关键参与者</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 11:23:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/under-the-cover-of-war-israel-is-moving-to-build-a-new-jewish-neighborhood-in-east-jlem/0000018d-9786-d9cc-a5cd-f7be43b10000</guid></item><item><title>警方逮捕了著名的以色列作家，抗议释放哈马斯扣押的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/police-arrest-esteemed-israeli-author-at-protest-for-release-of-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018d-97b3-d57f-a1ef-bfbf3d210000</link><description>以色列作家兼编辑奥娜·库辛 (Orna Coussin) 表示，在特拉维夫的一次示威活动中，抗议者与警察之间爆发肢体冲突，库辛的朋友遭到暴力袭击，她赶紧向朋友伸出援手。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 11:07:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/police-arrest-esteemed-israeli-author-at-protest-for-release-of-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018d-97b3-d57f-a1ef-bfbf3d210000</guid></item><item><title>与无意识对话：以色列人在手术期间减少谵妄</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-11/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-startup-making-communication-with-patients-under-anesthesia-possible/0000018d-97b1-d443-a19f-ffb1711f0000</link><description>以色列公司 EyeControl 开发了一种设备，可帮助医疗团队与从麻醉中醒来的患者保持联系，并可能有助于减少谵妄 ■ 加沙战争加剧了对该设备的需求</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 11:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2024-02-11/ty-article-magazine/the-israeli-startup-making-communication-with-patients-under-anesthesia-possible/0000018d-97b1-d443-a19f-ffb1711f0000</guid></item><item><title>Meta 关闭了伊朗领导人发布有关哈马斯和以色列的帖子的账户</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/meta-shuts-down-iranian-leaders-accounts-for-posts-on-hamas-israel/0000018d-974b-d57f-a1ef-bf5fb5af0000</link><description>霍梅尼因赞扬哈马斯而受到禁令之际，有报道称梅塔正在考虑如何管理滥用“犹太复国主义”一词的行为，因为它经常被用来指代犹太人或以色列人，而不仅仅是一种意识形态</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 09:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/meta-shuts-down-iranian-leaders-accounts-for-posts-on-hamas-israel/0000018d-974b-d57f-a1ef-bf5fb5af0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列考虑设立快速法庭审判 10 月 7 日或在加沙抓获的哈马斯恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-considers-fast-track-courts-for-hamas-members-captured-on-oct-7-or-in-gaza/0000018d-94d4-d443-a19f-fcd50e8c0000</link><description>该提案可能会引发对以色列在缺乏适当法律程序的情况下继续拘留被指控的哈马斯恐怖分子的批评，并对海牙产生影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 04:07:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-considers-fast-track-courts-for-hamas-members-captured-on-oct-7-or-in-gaza/0000018d-94d4-d443-a19f-fcd50e8c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡更喜欢加沙“全面胜利”的空洞口号，而不是以色列人质的生命</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/pm-prefers-hollow-slogans-about-decisive-win-over-lives-of-hostages/0000018d-94d9-d9cc-a5cd-f5fb0b2b0000</link><description>所有迹象都表明，以色列总理并不打算拿极右翼联盟的生存冒险来与哈马斯达成停火协议——对他来说，人质可以等待</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 04:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article/.premium/pm-prefers-hollow-slogans-about-decisive-win-over-lives-of-hostages/0000018d-94d9-d9cc-a5cd-f5fb0b2b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡誓言对加沙进行“安全控制”；拉法行动迫在眉睫，埃及警告以色列和哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article-live/idf-discovers-hamas-tunnels-weapons-under-unrwas-hq-in-gaza/0000018d-9600-d443-a19f-fe91a0240000</link><description>以色列国防军拉法地面入侵迫在眉睫，埃及威胁以色列和哈马斯 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：以色列对加沙地带的安全控制“在可预见的未来没有其他选择” ■ 拜登和内塔尼亚胡在美国对以色列在加沙的军事行为发出警告之际发表讲话 ■ 德国：以色列拉法的攻势将是“人道主义灾难”</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Feb 2024 03:56:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-11/ty-article-live/idf-discovers-hamas-tunnels-weapons-under-unrwas-hq-in-gaza/0000018d-9600-d443-a19f-fe91a0240000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，拉法行动尚未确定日期，公众言论可能会迫使哈马斯达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/sources-rafah-operation-public-discourse-could-pressure-hamas-toward-a-deal/0000018d-94b7-d9cc-a5cd-f5bf8b0e0000</link><description>国外消息人士称，埃及至加沙隧道尚未达成任何协议；确认人质谈判继续进行，以色列坚持巴黎商定的条款</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 21:25:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/sources-rafah-operation-public-discourse-could-pressure-hamas-toward-a-deal/0000018d-94b7-d9cc-a5cd-f5bf8b0e0000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡，我们不会给你片刻的和平”：抗议者封锁特拉维夫高速公路，纵火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/wont-give-netanyahu-a-moment-of-peace-protesters-block-tel-aviv-highway-start-a-fire/0000018d-9482-d57f-a1ef-bc9ef74f0000</link><description>示威者，包括被释放的人质和仍被加沙哈马斯扣押的人质的家人，聚集在以色列各地的几个地点，封锁了特拉维夫的主要高速公路，并与警察发生冲突。一名示威者在内塔尼亚胡的私人住宅外喊道，“把我们带到这个地方的人不适合管理这个国家”</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 20:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/wont-give-netanyahu-a-moment-of-peace-protesters-block-tel-aviv-highway-start-a-fire/0000018d-9482-d57f-a1ef-bc9ef74f0000</guid></item><item><title>“比比，我投票给你了。你什么时候会选择我？你什么时候会选择Matan？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/bibi-i-voted-for-you-when-will-you-choose-me-when-will-you-choose-matan/0000018d-9477-d443-a19f-fcf79f6b0000</link><description>周六举行的释放人质集会正值哈马斯扣押的人质中约有 50 人可能死亡的严峻消息，以及哈马斯提出的停火协议被中止，内塔尼亚胡总理认为该协议的条款不切实际且不可接受</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 20:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/bibi-i-voted-for-you-when-will-you-choose-me-when-will-you-choose-matan/0000018d-9477-d443-a19f-fcf79f6b0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔和沙特阿拉伯呼吁就以色列军队拉法入侵可能召开联合国安理会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/qatar-and-saudi-arabia-call-to-convene-un-security-council-over-possible-rafah-invasion/0000018d-93f7-d9cc-a5cd-f7ffade40000</link><description>哈马斯控制的卫生部表示，周六，44 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙南部城市拉法被杀，几小时前，内塔尼亚胡要求军方在地面入侵之前计划撤离那里的数十万人。</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 19:23:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/qatar-and-saudi-arabia-call-to-convene-un-security-council-over-possible-rafah-invasion/0000018d-93f7-d9cc-a5cd-f7ffade40000</guid></item></channel></rss>